.TH CGWATCHER 1 "November 2025" "0.1.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
cgwatcher \- TUI tool to monitor cgroup memory usage
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B cgwatcher
[\-\-interval \fISECONDS\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B cgwatcher
is a terminal user interface (TUI) that displays real-time memory usage, limits, and CPU quotas for cgroups in the user slice.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BR \-\-interval " " \fISECONDS\fR
Refresh interval in seconds (default: 1.0).
.TP
.BR \-\-app-scan-interval " " \fISECONDS\fR
Interval to rescan cgroup list in seconds (default: 2.0).
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR cgwatcherd (8)